    {
      "Text": "Security update for avahi",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for avahi fixes the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2026-24401: avahi-daemon can be crashed via a segmentation fault by sending an unsolicited mDNS response\n  containing a recursive CNAME record (bsc#1257235).\n",
